Title: Object: Fuite en Egypte
Description: Flight into Egypt: landscape with at centre the Virgin riding a donkey led by St Joseph, walking alongside a pond. 1848 Drypoint and roulette
Curator's comments: According to Guiffrey, only 12 impressions were made.
Bibliographic references: Guiffrey 1866 / L'Oeuvre de Charles Jacque: catalogue de ses eaux-fortes et pointes sèches (264.III)
